msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Uma ungaphandle kwe-US, sincoma i-NOWPayments (imali ezisezingeni eliphansi,"
" ngokuhambisana ne-wallet yakho). Uma ugxile e-US, i-Stripe Crypto nayo "
"iyindlela engcono. Ungavula izinsiza eziningi futhi uvumele abavakashi bakho"
" ukuthi bakhethe!"

