"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Imali yeCrypto yeStripe (USDC) iyatholakala kuphela kubhizinisi elisemazweni"
" aseMelika. Uma ungaphandle kweMelika, iStripe izokwamukela kuphela "
"izinkokhelo zekhadibhodi ku-Stripe balance (hhayi ngokuqondile ku-crypto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Uma uhlala eMelika, ungasebenzisa iStripe ukuthola i-crypto ngqo. Uma "
"ungaphandle, cabanga i-NOWPayments noma i-CoinGate ukuze ufinyelele ku-"
"crypto ngqo."

