msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"I-widget enamandla, engakhokhelwa, yokunikezela nokukhokha evumela "
"abavakashi bakho ukuthi bakweseke ngenkathi usebenzisa ikhadi lezezimali "
"noma i-cryptocurrency (Quai). Ayikho imithetho yenyanga, ayikho isabelomali "
"sangaphandle – yikwallet yakho nezinsiza ezikhululekile."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Ezinye iziphambili zivimba ama-scripts sangaphandle ngenxa yob privacy. Lo "
"msebenzi we-proxy uyaloads ama-scripts ngasendleleni ye-server yakho ukuze "
"uvikele lezi block."

msgid ""
"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"Ungabuyekeza ama-URL e-script ngezansi uma ama-URL asuselwa eguquke noma uma"
" ufuna ukusebenzisa i-CDN ehlukile."

